<plot>Year 3740; Planet Earth. 906 years have passed since the cataclysm of 2834. Only those that emigrated to the space-station survived the disaster. The waste left by Earth's previous occupiers has contaminated the atmosphere. My name is Truk and I am an Energy Hunter. The locator guides us towards Earth's great mountain, a perfect place for hunting clean energy. For a thousand years, my ancestors have hunted energy throughout this solar system but unfortunately our numbers are always decreasing. I can feel the energy close now I hope the hunter doesn't become the hunt.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?178573</url></doc>
